{"tid":2239911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被拘加國公民 9個月來首視像探望","createTime":"2020-10-12T10:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T10:07:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15284926c00f769840bb8df306f208b73b254d20","tid":2239911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/GAYIRZC3OFCYNA62Q6WGOTTVQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FGAYIRZC3OFCYNA62Q6WGOTTVQE%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=87329c73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FGAYIRZC3OFCYNA62Q6WGOTTVQE%2F&h=827c662b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/GAYIRZC3OFCYNA62Q6WGOTTVQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被拘加國公民 9個月來首視像探望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lZC3MImb_hgBGgetOiTEDB7UI3M=/1290x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FC4MTWWTHJF5BC3KJNIWLRBCDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlZC3MImb_hgBGgetOiTEDB7UI3M%3D%2F1290x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFC4MTWWTHJF5BC3KJNIWLRBCDQ.jpg&h=81722456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯帕沃<br />\n<br />\n加拿大外交部證實，駐華大使鮑達民（Dominic Barton）罕有獲准以視像形式，探望被中國扣留的前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）與商人斯帕沃（Michael Spavor）。這是兩人自1月，相隔九個月再獲領事探望。兩人因華為副董事長孟晚舟2018年12月1日在加拿大過境時被捕而遭中方報復，同年底在中國被捕並羈押至今。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大外交部10日發表聲明指，駐華大使鮑達民先後在上周五及上周六對斯帕沃與康明凱進行「虛擬領事探視」（virtual consular access）。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WyEjHhMyqJvI8IcqK8QnFhhlXE0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZHHWI36S5CM5AQSZGVE5QMPSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWyEjHhMyqJvI8IcqK8QnFhhlXE0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZHHWI36S5CM5AQSZGVE5QMPSU.jpg&h=5017d3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康明凱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟所獲待遇差天共地<br />\n<br />\n加國外交官在今年1月13日和14日獲准對探視兩人。兩人去年6月19日遭北京人民檢察院以「為境外刺探國家秘密、情報罪」起訴。兩人被捕迄今均未公開露面。而武肺疫情爆發後，加拿大駐華領使人員每月一次到看守所探望兩人的安排亦被暫停。<br />\n<br />\n法廣網指出，兩人在中國所受對待，與孟晚舟在加拿大獲得的待遇有天壤之別。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法廣網"}]}